In [[geometry]], the '''tritetratrigonal tiling''' or '''shieldotritetragonal tiling''' is a [[Uniform tilings in hyperbolic plane|uniform]] tiling of the [[Hyperbolic geometry|hyperbolic plane]]. It has [[Schläfli symbol]] of t<sub>1,2</sub>(4,3,3). It can also be named as a '''cantic [[octagonal tiling]]''', h<sub>2</sub>{8,3}.

